  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一张图来解释为什么州政府的医院系统总是承压。核心问题是联邦和州之间的责任错位，以及资金增长受限带来的连锁反应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Commonwealth responsibility",
        "State responsibility"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，您想突出两级政府之间的张力。我理解为三个层级：联邦的政策和收入工具、中间的摩擦缺口、以及州政府的实际运营端？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Commonwealth responsibility",
        "Interface friction",
        "State responsibility"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，正是这三个层级。联邦那边要包括税收收入、MBS、GP政策、老年护理和NDIS。这些是主要的政策杠杆。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Tax",
        "MBS",
        "GP",
        "AgedCare",
        "NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在左侧建了一个子图，标注为\"联邦职责（收入与政策杠杆）\"，里面放了Tax、MBS、GP、AgedCare和NDIS五个节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "Tax",
        "MBS",
        "GP",
        "AgedCare",
        "NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "中间这层最关键，叫\"接口摩擦\"吧。这里要放三个系统缺口：初级医疗可及性缺口、老年护理容量约束、NDIS支持延迟。还有这些缺口导致的后果——急诊不必要的就诊量和床位占用压力。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Gap1",
        "Gap2",
        "Gap3",
        "ED_Pres",
        "Bed_Occ"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "中间子图已建好，标注\"接口摩擦（成本转嫁/系统缺口）\"，包含Gap1、Gap2、Gap3、ED_Pres和Bed_Occ。这些节点我用虚线边框来突出风险感。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "F",
        "Gap1",
        "Gap2",
        "Gap3",
        "ED_Pres",
        "Bed_Occ"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
